text: David Brock (born 1962) is an American journalist and author. David Brock can also refer to: *Dave Brock (born 1941), English musician *D. Brock Hornby (born 1944), American federal judge from Maine *Dave Brock (American football) (born 1967), American football coach *David Brock (lacrosse) (born 1986), Canadian lacrosse player *David Brock, character in 2011 British audio drama The Feast of Axos == See also == * David Brockhoff (1928–2011), Australian rugby player called Brock * David Brock Smith, Oregon state representative * Dave Brockie, Canadian heavy metal musician
